If your game is the winner, we'll roll out the red carpet and give you the VIP treatment. You'll get extensive coverage before, during and after the big game! Tune in to 11Alive News at 6, #Team11 at 10:30 p.m. on TheATL and 11Alive News at 11 to see yourself on TV! Plus, highlights will live forever right here on 11Alive.com.
